<h1>Education & Training Resources</h1>

<p class="intro">
    Explore our curated collection of educational materials to boost your knowledge in sustainable agriculture, farm management, and hands-on techniques. Whether you're just starting out or looking to refine your skills, there's something here for every grower.
</p>

<div class="resource-section">
    <h2>🌐 Online Courses</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/sustainable-agriculture" target="_blank">Introduction to Sustainable Agriculture</a> – Learn about environmentally responsible farming practices on Coursera.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.edx.org/course/farm-business-management" target="_blank">Farm Business Management Basics</a> – Understand financial planning and decision-making via edX.</li>
        <li><a href="https://extension.psu.edu/soil-health-principles" target="_blank">Soil Health and Fertility</a> – Penn State Extension’s free guide to improving soil productivity.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="resource-section">
    <h2>📅 Webinars & Workshops</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.nrcs.usda.gov/events/climate-smart-agriculture-webinar" target="_blank">Upcoming: Climate-Smart Farming</a> – Register now for this live USDA webinar on sustainable practices.</li>
        <li><a href="https://attra.ncat.org/product/irrigation-efficiency/" target="_blank">Workshop: Irrigation Techniques for Small Farms</a> – Attend a virtual or in-person workshop hosted by ATTRA.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kzwpGzvKxlc" target="_blank">Recorded Webinar: Pest Management Strategies</a> – Watch this past session from the University of California Agriculture & Natural Resources.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="resource-section">
    <h2>📺 YouTube Videos & Tutorials</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fRlUhUWS0Hk" target="_blank">How to Start Organic Farming</a> – A beginner-friendly guide to setting up an organic farm.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eGT8jrLzzJw" target="_blank">Top 5 Crops for Beginners</a> – Learn which crops are most profitable and easy to grow.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FJF49lb23b8" target="_blank">DIY Drip Irrigation Setup</a> – Step-by-step tutorial for building your own irrigation system at low cost.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
